MBOMBELA &#8211; An accident on the Long Tom Pass left 23 people seriously injured and seven with minor injuries earlier today.According to ER 24&#8217;s Greg Wilcox there were no fatalities.This was confirmed in a statement issued by spokesman for the Department of Community, Safety, Security and Liaison, Joseph Mabuza.According to Wilcox ER24 treated 15 patients on the scene.